      "biography": {
        "value": "<p><em>Greeting: \"The frigid veil persists.\" | Response: \"All the world in winter's white.\" | Parting: \"May her blessing chill you.\"</em></p><p>Tempests have proved themselves by providing food and shelter to another member \u2014 a delicate balance given the tenets of isolation. They mark themselves with permanent tattoos or brands. Brutal enforcers who threaten anyone voicing disapproval of the Frostmaiden. Actively infiltrate the Zhentarim and Knights of the Black Sword.</p><p><strong>Renown 3 | CR 1/2</strong></p>"
